note_tsim: Five perspective views of the approaches to New York Harbor taken by J.F.W. Des Barres for the use of Royal Navy of Great Britain.
Appears to be an early state, with a limited amount of vessels appearing only in the last three views.
From vol. 5 of Des Barres's Atlantic Neptune.
